{"tid":2214480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"去年大埔墟站11人被指非法集結 一年後遭起訴 警方仍未完成草擬案情交予控辯雙方","createTime":"2020-09-23T09:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:31:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13bb861955900827f03a4c2723858dbad3c712ab","tid":2214480,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:35:06.000Z","msg":"約200名大埔街坊去年9月7日計劃在港鐵站手拖手築人鏈，聲援機場「和你飛」行動，有少年在大埔墟站內遭群警亂棍扑爆頭，頭破血流倒地。當晚有市民被指在站內聚集，因而被捕，部份人受查後踢保。惟事隔一年，警方重新拘捕及起訴11人，控以11項非法集結罪，其中10人是學生，有兩名被告為父女。案件今午在西九龍裁判法院提堂，各人繼續保釋，等候答辯。<br />\n<br />\n案件應辯方要求押後答辯，以便檢視相關證據及影片。各被告繼續准以500元現金保釋至12月30日再訊，其間不得離港，每星期向警署報到一次。三名未滿18歲的未成年被告，須每晚11時至翌晨6時宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n案發至今已逾一年，據庭外了解，控辯雙方仍未收到警方草擬的案情撮要，暫未能掌握案發情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/KDB4YTXKABE5HJS4B6XVOOU3G4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FKDB4YTXKABE5HJS4B6XVOOU3G4%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9lcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=d93c4200\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FKDB4YTXKABE5HJS4B6XVOOU3G4%2F&h=aca62913\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/KDB4YTXKABE5HJS4B6XVOOU3G4/</a>"},{"pid":"22347542789f056579f404baf5afeea2e7a3ba9b","tid":2214480,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac46019a5c4fa69813109c3b15f2992bdeb448cb","tid":2214480,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T09:37:08.000Z","msg":"//<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>案發至今已逾一年，據庭外了解，控辯雙方仍未收到警方草擬的案情撮要</strong></span></span>，暫未能掌握案發情況。//<br />\n<br />\n作成年都作唔到份劇本出嚟啊!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},